As of the [[2020 United States census]], there were 474 people, 316 households, and 183 families residing in the town.<ref>{{Cite web|title=S1101 HOUSEHOLDS AND FAMILIES - 2020: Beverly Beach town, Florida|url=https://data.census.gov/table?q=Beverly+Beach+town;+Florida+&tid=ACSST5Y2020.S1101|website=[[United States Census Bureau]]}}</ref>

As of the [[2010 United States census]], there were 338 people, 249 households, and 147 families residing in the town.<ref>{{Cite web|title=S1101 HOUSEHOLDS AND FAMILIES - 2010: Beverly Beach town, Florida|url=https://data.census.gov/table?q=Beverly+Beach+town;+Florida+&tid=ACSST5Y2010.S1101|website=[[United States Census Bureau]]}}</ref>

